AttributeSupport - Interface in org.trustedcomputinggroup.tnc.ifimc
These methods can be implemented by an object in the IMC package to get or set attributes.

B

batchEnding(IMCConnection) - Method in interface org.trustedcomputinggroup.tnc.ifimc.IMC
The TNC Client calls this method to notify IMCs that all IMV messages received in a batch have been delivered and this is the IMC's last chance to send a message in the batch of IMC messages currently being collected.
beginHandshake(IMCConnection) - Method in interface org.trustedcomputinggroup.tnc.ifimc.IMC
The TNC Client calls this method to indicate that an Integrity Check Handshake is beginning and solicit messages from IMCs for the first batch.

IMCConnection - Interface in org.trustedcomputinggroup.tnc.ifimc

IMCSOH - Interface in org.trustedcomputinggroup.tnc.ifimc
